           	<td valign="top" height="100%"><font face="arial" size="2" color="#000000">
                      <font face="arial" size="2" color="#000000"><span class="spnMessageText" id="msg"> Currently 36 Nec, soloing in OT.  Using Fear Kite method.  My question is this:<br /><br />Is it better to use Fearinstead of Invoke Fear?<br /><br />What I have observed:<br /><br /> <ul><li>Invoke makes the mobs run much farther away, causing me to chase them down</li><li>With casting cost of 100, fizzles and resists are costing me entirely too much of my mana bar</li><br /><li>Fear has the mobs almost constantly in range of any spell I want to cast</li></ul><br /><br />However, the mobs seem to shrug normal Fear off at a much greater rate.<br /><br />Any comments/help on this would be greatly appreciated.</span id="msg"></font>
           	</td>
                    </tr>
